    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Adding 'and a half' and 'and a quarter'"
        },
        "text": "To specify half past or a quarter past the hour, you add 'ونص' (w noss) for half and 'وربع' (w rob') for a quarter after the hour.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "الساعة الجوج ونص",
            "english": "Half past two (2:30)",
            "transliteration": "Ess-sa'a j-jūj w noss"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "الساعة الخمسة وربع",
            "english": "Quarter past five (5:15)",
            "transliteration": "Ess-sa'a l-khemsa w rob'"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Adding 'to a quarter' and 'minutes past/to'"
        },
        "text": "For a quarter to the hour, use 'إلا ربع' (illa rob'). For specific minutes, 'ودقيقة/ودقايق' (w dqiqa/w dqayeq) means 'and X minutes' and 'إلا دقيقة/إلا دقايق' (illa dqiqa/illa dqayeq) means 'X minutes to'. 'دقيقة' is singular, 'دقايق' is plural.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "الساعة السبعة إلا ربع",
            "english": "A quarter to seven (6:45)",
            "transliteration": "Ess-sa'a s-seb'a illa rob'"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "الساعة العشرة وعشرين دقيقة",
            "english": "Ten twenty (10:20)",
            "transliteration": "Ess-sa'a l-'ashra w 'ashrin dqiqa"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "الساعة الحداش إلا خمسة دقايق",
            "english": "Five minutes to eleven (10:55)",
            "transliteration": "Ess-sa'a l-Hdash illa khemsa dqayeq"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Time of Day: Morning, Afternoon, Evening"
        },
        "text": "To specify the time of day, you can add words like 'الصباح' (es-sbah) for morning, 'العشية' (el-'ashiya) for afternoon, and 'الليل' (el-lil) for evening/night.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "الساعة السبعة د الصباح",
            "english": "Seven in the morning (7 AM)",
            "transliteration": "Ess-sa'a s-seb'a d es-sbah"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "الجوج د العشية",
            "english": "Two in the afternoon (2 PM)",
            "transliteration": "J-jūj d el-'ashiya"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "العشرة د الليل",
            "english": "Ten at night (10 PM)",
            "transliteration": "El-'ashra d el-lil"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
